==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: off-the-shelf
<hw>off-the-shelf</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Made in large quantities and
intended to be used without modifications; -- similar to
<contr>off-the-rack</contr>, but not restricted to clothing. Opposite of
<ant>custom-made</ant>, <ant>made-to-order</ant>, or
<ant>one-of-a-kind</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

